<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for your purchase! We’re excited to let you know that your order has been successfully placed and paid for with <strong>cash on delivery</strong>.</p>

      <p>Your order is now being processed, and you’ll receive updates as soon as it ships.</p>

      <a href="http://yourshop.com/orders/<%= id %>" class="btn">View Your Order</a>

      <p>We truly appreciate your business and look forward to serving you again.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br />
      <strong>The Ecommerce-NestJS Team</strong></p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, contact our support at <a href="mailto:support@ecommerce-nestjs.com">support@ecommerce-nestjs.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
